<h2 id="数据统计与分析"><a href="#数据统计与分析" class="headerlink" title="数据统计与分析"></a>数据统计与分析</h2><h3 id="不蒜子统计"><a href="#不蒜子统计" class="headerlink" title="不蒜子统计"></a>不蒜子统计</h3><p>由于我使用的next5.0.1已经集成了“不蒜子统计”，所以直接去next的_config.yml里面修改：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ vim _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">busuanzi_count:</span><br><span class="line">  # count values only if the other configs are false</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # custom uv span for the whole site</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv: true</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_header: 本站访客数</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_footer: 人次</span><br><span class="line">  # custom pv span for the whole site</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv: true</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_header: 本站总访问量</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_footer: 次</span><br><span class="line">  # custom pv span for one page only</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv: true</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_header: 本文总阅读量</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_footer: 次</span><br><span class="line">:wq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="阅读次数统计（LeanCloud）"><a href="#阅读次数统计（LeanCloud）" class="headerlink" title="阅读次数统计（LeanCloud）"></a>阅读次数统计（LeanCloud）</h3><p>前面不蒜子统计虽然也可以实现这个功能，但是不蒜子只能在文章内显示阅读量，而不能在主页显示阅读量，所以这里来使用LeanCloud来完成这个功能。  </p>
<h4 id="配置LeanCloud"><a href="#配置LeanCloud" class="headerlink" title="配置LeanCloud"></a>配置LeanCloud</h4><h5 id="创建应用"><a href="#创建应用" class="headerlink" title="创建应用"></a>创建应用</h5><p>打开<a href="https://leancloud.cn/" target="_blank" rel="external">LeanCloud</a>，注册，验证，登陆账号，进行一番操作，最后拿到AppID以及AppKey这两个参数即可正常使用文章阅读量统计的功能了。下面是具体操作：<br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/69C417382DAC42CBA1230406938EF42C/71254" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/92ABF3D879C647E89F32B1140ACB7FB2/71258" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/7292BC581D4F4D998DFBF19698BB3B7E/71262" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/F4EF032191C14921BA28C3EC183C65F9/71266" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/C64A280CB3554187A90223A0F6328202/71268" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/4D17E3279CEC487FB4C110AB2D9D211B/71272" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/B3554A609E584E6D807A5BDFC6B53F56/71276" alt=""><br>现在我们已经看到了App ID和App Key，下面去修改我的NexT主题的配置文件_config.yml<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ vim _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">leancloud_visitors:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  app_id: 2ynxyDtFk1g8s6cspe1R5uIF-gzGzoHsz</span><br><span class="line">  app_key: AV9DiP0JsjB1kCbthacoDnh6</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#新建一篇文章测试一下效果</span></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo n <span class="string">"new test"</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: D:\GitHub\hexo\<span class="built_in">source</span>\_posts\new-test.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="built_in">source</span>/_posts/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/<span class="built_in">source</span>/_posts</span><br><span class="line">$ ll</span><br><span class="line">total 5</span><br><span class="line">-rw-r--r-- 1 JUN 197121 864 五月 21 12:23 hello-world.md</span><br><span class="line">-rw-r--r-- 1 JUN 197121  56 九月 20 20:35 new-test.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/<span class="built_in">source</span>/_posts</span><br><span class="line">$ vim new-test.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/<span class="built_in">source</span>/_posts</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start processing</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000/. Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>来看一下效果，已经可以了，那么可以关闭不蒜子的这部分统计功能了。<br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/38500F5A973F458C89DCF281E6E12BC0/71803" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/1ACC919F7C5848ECBB33FE41DDEF3518/71801" alt=""><br>关闭不蒜子的“本文总阅读量”统计功能：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ vim _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">busuanzi_count:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># count values only if the other configs are false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># custom uv span for the whole site</span></span><br><span class="line">  site_uv: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_header: 本站访客数</span><br><span class="line">  site_uv_footer: 人次</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># custom pv span for the whole site</span></span><br><span class="line">  site_pv: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_header: 本站总访问量</span><br><span class="line">  site_pv_footer: 次</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># custom pv span for one page only</span></span><br><span class="line">  page_pv: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_header: 本文总阅读量</span><br><span class="line">  page_pv_footer: 次</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h5 id="后台管理"><a href="#后台管理" class="headerlink" title="后台管理"></a>后台管理</h5><p>我们可以在后台手工修改文章的访问次数（time），以达到提升Bigger的目的。<br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/62E91B3C80FA40C4AC28E8AA8637179D/71821" alt=""><br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/D53F59932E934C5A86FBA11A2D7AD502/71831" alt="">   </p>
<h5 id="Web安全"><a href="#Web安全" class="headerlink" title="Web安全"></a>Web安全</h5><p>因为AppID和AppKey是暴露在外的，很不安全，如果被小坏人知道了就麻烦了，所以我们这里来限制一下只有我们自己的博客域名才可以访问后台，这样会提升安全性。<br><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/93CA9CFF545F4C7498ABB32DE7E1E619/71837" alt="">  </p>
<h3 id="本地搜索服务"><a href="#本地搜索服务" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索服务"></a>本地搜索服务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo-generator-search@1.0.2 node_modules\hexo-generator-search</span><br><span class="line">├── utils-merge@1.0.0</span><br><span class="line">└── ejs@1.0.0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="百度分享"><a href="#百度分享" class="headerlink" title="百度分享"></a>百度分享</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ vim _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">baidushare:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: button</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/5f8ab6eb732698d9552af54e1971bcc5/xmlnote/C367981020AC424690CA9AB75D2F411E/71966" alt="">  </p>
<h3 id="友盟U-Web-CNZZ统计"><a href="#友盟U-Web-CNZZ统计" class="headerlink" title="友盟U-Web/CNZZ统计"></a>友盟U-Web/CNZZ统计</h3><p>CNZZ现在已经合并到友盟+了，原来的产品该名称叫友盟U-Web了。去友盟+注册账号，选择产品友盟U-Web，立即使用，填写一些你的博客域名信息后会得到一个siteid=1260437617（看地址栏），把这个siteid的值填写到next主题的配置文件中。<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ vim _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">cnzz_siteid: 1260437617</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>测试了一下，竟然不生效，那就直接贴代码吧。登录友盟+，进入你的U-Web产品，复制你的统计代码，添加代码到hexo/themes/next/layout/_partials/<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JUN@JUN-PC  /d/GitHub/hexo/themes/next/layout/_partials (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ vim footer.swig</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;% <span class="keyword">if</span> theme.cnzz_siteid %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;span class=<span class="string">"site-pv"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;script <span class="built_in">type</span>=<span class="string">"text/javascript"</span>&gt;var cnzz_protocol = ((<span class="string">"https:"</span> == document.location.protocol) ? <span class="string">" https://"</span> : <span class="string">" http://"</span>);document.write(unescape(<span class="string">"%3Cspan id='cnzz_stat_icon_1260437617'%3E%3C/span%3E%3Cscript src='"</span> + cnzz_protocol + <span class="string">"s11.cnzz.com/z_stat.php%3Fid%3D1260437617%26show%3Dpic' type='text/javascript'%3E%3C/script%3E"</span>));&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
